name: Zuckuss
Lore: 'Male Gand. Practitioner of ancient religious findsman vocation. Bounty hunter and scout. Gains surprisingly accurate information through mystical visions during meditation.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. May move for free as a ''react.'' Once during each battle, may use 1 Force to cause one alien of ability < 3 at same site to be forfeit = 0 for remainder of turn. Immune to attrition < 3.',
